That's enough. Even a dog shouldn't
be bothered when he's eating.

45
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:56,190
How can you treat
your little brother like this?

46
00:04:56,590 --> 00:04:58,530
Gosh, my head. You're killing me.

47
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:01,400
I feel so bad for myself that
you're the only family I have.

48
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:17,910
You little...

49
