However, I won't be putting
the mint candy in the soda.

54
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:42,270
I'll put them into my mouth first.
I've already peeled many of them.

55
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:45,640
I'll dump all of them into my mouth
and drink the soda in one minute.

56
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:47,540
Jeong-hun, dinner is ready.

57
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,909
I don't want to eat. I'm full.

58
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,780
All right. Then,

59
00:05:53,010 --> 00:05:56,280
What? I should just eat dinner
because it's an impossible mission?

60
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,090
You go eat your dinner, okay?

61
00:05:58,150 --> 00:06:01,160
All right, everyone.
I never give up.

62
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:03,390
I can eat everything.
I'll eat them all.

63
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:06,560
Then I'll peel the last pack
of mint candy I have.

64
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,700
I'm getting nervous.

65
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:12,230
Jeong-hun, come and eat!

66
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,170
