during my show?

69
00:06:18,710 --> 00:06:22,080
My viewers' love is enough
to fill me up, okay?

70
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:26,410
All right. I'll open the bottle
of soda now. Here we go.

71
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:31,750
Okay, the bottle is now open.

72
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:34,320
