79
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,780
Mom, my show is on. Let's go eat.

80
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,920
You little...

81
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:06,150
-Come before I smack your head.
-All right. Let's go, Mom.

82
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:07,890
Just a minute, okay?
I'll be right back.

83
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,190
Shut it! You're not coming back.

84
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:10,730
Don't forget to send me stars
if you like my show!

85
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,810
What do you think?
Do you like the house?

86
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:33,380
Yes, of course.
I don't know how to thank you properly.

87
00:07:33,450 --> 00:07:35,650
