-You must be tired.
-Don't worry.

104
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:21,430
-I'm fine.
-Honey, where should I put this?

105
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,870
Oh, that? It should go
in the master bedroom.

106
00:08:23,930 --> 00:08:26,230
All right, I'll leave it
in the master bedroom.

107
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,940
By the way, you guys have...

108
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,470
