109
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,670
-I'll carry it.
-Please have a seat.

110
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:33,070
-I can do it.
-It's okay.

111
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:34,179
Thank you.

112
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,409
We should get going now.

113
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,720
Gosh, why are you leaving already?

114
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:42,480
