to help the homeless.

118
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:54,160
It'd be so good to have
young people like you guys on board.

119
00:08:54,930 --> 00:08:57,800
-Don't you think so?
-My gosh, that'd be amazing.

120
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:59,570
