to participate in it?

124
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,780
-Pardon?
-Dad,

125
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:11,110
we haven't finished unpacking.

126
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,420
You helped us so much.

127
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:17,790
