you also have a beautiful heart.

145
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,650
Are you ready?

146
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:26,690
(-Are your pigs doing well?
-Yes.)

147
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:32,830
Hello. How have you been these days?

148
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,100
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

149
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,070
Thank you.

150
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,150
Let's help the needy.

151
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:54,550
Here you go, ma'am.

152
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:55,980
Thank you.

153
00:10:56,050 --> 00:10:57,090
Excuse me.

154
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:58,820
I need to go to the bathroom.

155
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:01,960
Oh, really? There's one over there.

156
00:11:04,490 --> 00:11:05,690
Have some tea.

157
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,930
He must've held it in for a while.

158
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:14,670
Hello. Hi.

159
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:17,570
Here. Thank you.

160
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:37,130
Gosh, that girl from Seoul
is so provoking.

161
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:39,290
Is she looking down on us
because we're from Muji?

162
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,460
It's not because she was
looking down on you.

163
00:11:41,530 --> 00:11:43,870
It's because you have no manners.

164
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,670
