178
00:12:20,770 --> 00:12:23,000
-Let me see.
-Move.

179
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:25,640
-Let's see.
-Don't do this.

180
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:28,340
-Don't move.
-Are you embarrassed

181
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:29,440
because of her?

182
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:32,050
