183
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,650
Go and lock the door.

184
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:35,250
Keep going.

185
00:12:35,950 --> 00:12:37,450
Move your hand. Come on.

186
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,890
Let me see.

187
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:40,760
Stop it. Please stop.

188
00:12:53,430 --> 00:12:54,470
Sang-jin.

189
00:12:57,010 --> 00:12:58,010
Are you okay?

190
00:12:58,670 --> 00:12:59,670
