197
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:30,540
No, I'm fine.

198
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:32,770
I heard that twins are able
to understand each other

199
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,010
even without having to talk
to one another.

200
00:13:35,110 --> 00:13:37,210
Is it really true that
you guys can

201
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,850
