even when he doesn't say anything.

203
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:45,320
I envy you, Sang-jin.

204
00:13:46,350 --> 00:13:48,560
You have such a pretty sister.

205
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:51,860
Sang-jin.

206
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,800
