215
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:23,120
Yes, we do. See you next time.

216
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:26,060
You did great today.
I hope you take some rest.

217
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,400
Okay.

218
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:28,560
Let's go.

219
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:30,700
Okay.

220
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:36,540
Let's eat together next time.

221
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:46,880
-Sang-jin.
-What?

222
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:48,450
Something happened earlier, right?

223
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:51,650
No, nothing happened.

224
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,250
Stop lying to me.

225
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:55,990
Sang-mi.

226
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:59,530
Mom and Dad are going through
a lot right now.

227
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:01,700
So please don't say anything to them.

228
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:05,000
Please.

229
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:10,000
Okay.

230
00:15:20,110 --> 00:15:25,450
