00:56:37,420 --> 00:56:38,760
Sang-jin.

785
00:56:38,820 --> 00:56:40,990
(REST IN PEACE)

786
00:56:41,090 --> 00:56:43,860
Sang-jin.

787
00:56:48,570 --> 00:56:49,570
I'm so sorry.

788
00:56:52,700 --> 00:56:54,470
It's all my fault.

789
00:56:58,380 --> 00:57:00,550
Dad is so sorry
for everything, Sang-jin.

790
00:57:12,820 --> 00:57:14,530
I'm sorry for your loss.

791
00:57:16,460 --> 00:57:19,360
I don't even know what to say.

792
00:57:20,470 --> 00:57:21,530
My heart

793
00:57:22,970 --> 00:57:24,440
breaks for you and your family.

794
00:57:25,170 --> 00:57:26,610
Please don't worry about us.

795
00:57:27,570 --> 00:57:29,710
The fact that you came here like this

796
00:57:30,440 --> 00:57:33,510
is enough to make us grateful.

797
00:57:35,280 --> 00:57:36,450
I'm sure Sang-jin is

798
00:57:37,380 --> 00:57:38,950
resting in peace

799
00:57:40,390 --> 00:57:41,990
in the arms of the Almighty.

800
00:57:42,120 --> 00:57:43,160
From now on,

801
00:57:43,960 --> 00:57:45,820
we will protect you like family.

802
00:57:46,860 --> 00:57:48,460
Thank you.

803
00:57:53,170 --> 00:57:57,040
Ms. Kim. This must be
very painful to you too,

804
00:57:58,070 --> 00:57:59,240
but

805
00:58:00,210 --> 00:58:02,040
for Sang-mi's sake,

806
00:58:03,080 --> 00:58:04,680
you should pull yourself together.

807
00:58:30,900 --> 00:58:33,040
I remember Sang-jin as a boy

808
00:58:33,870 --> 00:58:37,510
who prayed in the empty hall alone

809
00:58:38,940 --> 00:58:41,980
even though he lost
the use of his one leg.

810
00:58:43,080 --> 00:58:44,580
He was a warm-hearted

811
00:58:46,620 --> 00:58:48,450
and beautiful boy.

812
00:58:58,660 --> 00:58:59,770
However,

813
00:59:02,470 --> 00:59:05,570
after hearing the news
about Sang-jin today,

814
00:59:08,370 --> 00:59:10,580
I couldn't pray at all.

815
00:59:12,910 --> 00:59:13,980
Everyone.

816
00:59:14,710 --> 00:59:17,080
I'd like to stand here today

817
00:59:18,020 --> 00:59:20,550
as a human being,

818
00:59:20,690 --> 00:59:22,650
not a cleric.

819
00:59:23,220 --> 00:59:26,990
And I'd like to ask the Almighty.

820
00:59:34,070 --> 00:59:35,270
Why?

821
00:59:37,940 --> 00:59:41,270
Why on earth did you take

822
00:59:42,710 --> 00:59:44,110
that precious child?

823
00:59:46,310 --> 00:59:47,950
Why couldn't you

824
00:59:48,710 --> 00:59:52,350
(protect the soul of
that precious child)

825
00:59:52,420 --> 00:59:54,820
(with your power?)

826
00:59:56,050 --> 01:00:00,590
You told me you will save

827
01:00:01,460 --> 01:00:05,100
your child suffering in agony, so why?

828
01:00:07,930 --> 01:00:09,670
Why did you take him away?

829
01:00:17,380 --> 01:00:18,640
Almighty.

830
01:00:21,850 --> 01:00:23,110
I really

831
01:00:24,050 --> 01:00:26,890
resent you for doing this.

832
01:00:38,400 --> 01:00:40,230
Please answer me!

833
01:00:41,100 --> 01:00:43,370
What is your intention?

834
01:00:43,700 --> 01:00:47,740
Why didn't you answer
your child's prayers?

835
01:00:48,040 --> 01:00:50,280
Why did you have to

836
01:00:50,340 --> 01:00:54,480
break this family's hearts so painfully?

837
01:00:59,220 --> 01:01:00,790
I must

838
01:01:02,220 --> 01:01:04,460
hear your answers.

839
01:01:08,530 --> 01:01:11,660
This child cried out to you

840
01:01:11,860 --> 01:01:15,900
and asked you to save him
so desperately!

841
01:01:16,100 --> 01:01:19,440
Did you really turn away from it?

842
01:01:45,030 --> 01:01:47,670
(SAVE ME)

843
01:01:52,300 --> 01:01:53,440
(Sang-jin.)

844
01:01:54,370 --> 01:01:55,540
(I promise.)

845
01:02:00,080 --> 01:02:02,050
(I promise I will
take your revenge on them.)
